== Reading ExtJs in Action with the aid of Rwt

A Rails application using coding examples from the book

  ExtJs in Action
  Jay Garcia
  Manning

Permission to reproduce parts of the book given by J. Garcia
http://twitter.com/smbrant/status/13089787173
http://twitter.com/tdgi/status/13095918954

== Putting this application to work

$ git clone git://github.com/smbrant/readingextjsinaction.git
$ cd readingextjsinaction
$ mkdir log
$ mkdir tmp
$ mkdir -p vendor/plugins
$ cd public
$ wget http://www.extjs.com/deploy/ext-3.2.1.zip
$ unzip ext-3.2.1.zip
$ mv ext-3.2.1 ext
$ rm ext-3.2.1.zip
$ cd ../vendor/plugins
$ git clone git://github.com/smbrant/rwt.git
$ cd ../..
$ ruby script/server

Go to http://localhost:3000

